ut string.\n```\n"]}, {"name": "cosmic_toolbox.utils.parse_sequence", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "s", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Parses a string to a list/tuple for argparse. Can be used as type for argparse.\n\n```\nparam s\n\nString to parse.\n\nreturn\n\ntuple or list.\n\nraises argparse.ArgumentTypeError\n\nIf the string cannot be parsed to a tuple.\n```\n"]}, {"name": "cosmic_toolbox.utils.parse_list", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "s", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Parses a string to a list for argparse. Can be used as type for argparse.\n\n```\nparam s\n\nString to parse.\n\nreturn\n\nlist.\n```\n"]}, {"name": "cosmic_toolbox.utils.is_between", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "x", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "min", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "max", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Checks if x is between min and max.\n\n```\nparam x\n\nValue to check.\n\nparam min\n\nMinimum value.\n\nparam max\n\nMaximum value.\n\nreturn\n\nTrue if x is between min and max, False otherwise.\n```\n"]}, {"name": "cosmic_toolbox.utils.run_imap_multiprocessing", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "func", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "argument_list", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "num_processes", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "verb", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Runs a function with a list of arguments in parallel using multiprocessing.\n\n```\nparam func\n\nFunction to run.\n\nparam argument_list\n\nList of arguments to run the function with.\n\nparam num_processes\n\nNumber of processes to use.\n\nparam verb\n\nIf True, show progress bar.\n\nreturn\n\nList of results from the function.\n```\n"]}], "variables": [{"name": "cosmic_toolbox.utils.LOGGER", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []},